title: Binance makes return into Japan under a new subsidiary
description: After an absence of five years, cryptocurrency exchange Binance is making a comeback in the Japanese market. The company has initiated the process of establishing a new subsidiary that will operate under full regulation in the country. This development follows the exchange’s acquisition of Sakura Exchange Bitcoin (SEBC), a regulated cryptocurrency exchange, in November 2022. ... Read more
